thread.title: Ireland vote ends abortion ban in 'quiet revolution'

title: Ireland vote ends abortion ban in 'quiet revolution'
text:
Ireland vote ends abortion ban in 'quiet revolution' 1:48pm EDT - 01:53
Ireland's referendum on abortion has led to a landslide victory for those trying to liberalize the country's restrictive abortion laws. The country's Prime Minister Leo Varadkar has called it the culmination of a 'quiet revolution'
